OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Feasing for most, with cloud breaks
OL,7,Fdeveloping. The odd mist or fog
OL,8,Fpatches could then form, and it will
OL,9,Fbe feeling rather cool with light
OL,10,Fwinds. The odd pocket of rural frost
OL,11,Fcannot be completely ruled out.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FMostly fine, with variable
OL,14,Famounts of cloud and some sunny
OL,15,Fspells. Easterly winds will gradually
OL,16,Fstrengthen through the day, leading to
OL,17,Fa cooler feel, especially along
OL,18,FEnglish Channel coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
